About this game
Relax and find peace as you complete joyful artworks by pushing diamonds onto a canvas.

Simply follow the numbers and paint as quickly or slowly as you like - thrill to the satisfying ‘click’ as the diamond finds its place. Watch your masterpiece sparkle with each color you complete.

A soothing, zen experience that is sure to leave you happy and mindful.
